ygData.messageBody:
There are 2 schools of thought regarding where to
go in your Late teens early Twenties. Here's what i
did (this is for a Barb Shaman) 15-18 Oasis, at 18 I
went to Lake Rathe and started on Aviaks and then
moved up to Gnolls i went from 18 to 24 here Very
Quickly, after 24 SK (its just outside) and got a spire
group. You can easliy go from 24 - 30 at the spires.
LOIO is a great zone and you can go all the way to 30
there, but i think that until 24 Lake Rathe is the
best..<br><br>Nyk..<br>Knowledge is Power. Power Corrupts. Study Hard. Be Evil.
